data.name: Double Fin Shark
data.desc: When this card is Normal Summoned: You can target 1 Level 3 or 4 WATER Fish-Type monster in your Graveyard; Special Summon that target in Defense Position, but it has its effects negated. You cannot Special Summon any monsters during the turn you activate this effect, except WATER monsters.

card_sets.set_name: Legendary Duelists: Duels From the Deep
